s // N\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"eccb8010-5a00-49f4-845e-4fe02cf08c97"],

Cell["\<\
t := betah/s
t // N\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"bdc68432-1eeb-452e-a78b-9ab1a7bd0b5d"],

Cell["\<\
