\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"6b2687b1-4577-4b07-b15b-805f2b5a8471"],

Cell["Reduce[c1 a1 + c2 a2 == {0, 0}]", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"b49466a9-f0cd-4321-8363-188a985b2593"],

Cell["\<\
